Name: The Conners
Title: Birthdays, Babies and Emotional Support Chickens
Desc: It's Beverly Rose's birthday, but Becky and Emilio disagree on what kind of party they should have.
LongDescription: It's Beverly Rose's first birthday -- but it's not all cake and candles -- when Becky and Emilio disagree on what kind of party they should have; Jackie is introduced to someone who wants to be more than friends.
